Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[telegram] <mo7881> yes and no. to get rewards the KMD needs to be in your agama wallet, they accrue slowly, 0.0069 % per hour .
You can transfer to Agama, get rewards over time and send them back to Ledger whenever you want, but once they are in your ledger you wont get rewards going forward. (re @Gudneh: For me to receive the active user rewards can't I just transfer the funds to a new agama wallet get the rewards and then move them back?)
